<h1 id="-populateall-query-">.populateAll( [<code>query</code>] )</h1>
<h3 id="purpose" permalink="purpose">Purpose</h3>
<p>This chainable method is used between .find()/.update() and .exec() in order to retrieve records associated with the model being queried.  All known associations of your model will be populated and the query will be applied to each of them.</p>
